Package: bergreg
Type: Package
Title: BerG Regression for Count Data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Rodrigo",
           family = "Medeiros",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "rodrigo.matheus@live.com")
Description: A regression model for modeling overdispersed,
    equidispersed, and underdispersed count data, where
    it is assumed that dependent variables are
    distributed according to the BerG distribution.
